44 bonus is paid, after attaining one of the following:
45 1. The age of at least 65 with five years of creditable service.
46 2. The age of at least 60 with 25 years of creditable service.
47 3. Thirty years of creditable service.
48 SECTION 7A.3.(c) Advanced Course Bonuses. – A bonus in the amount of fifty
49 dollars ($50.00) shall be provided to qualifying advanced course teachers for each student taught
50 in each advanced course who receives the following score:
