23 in the 2025-2027 fiscal biennium to any principal who supervised a school as a principal for a
24 majority of the previous school year if that school was in the top fifty percent (50%) of school
25 growth in the State during the previous school year, calculated by the State Board pursuant to
26 G.S. 115C-83.15(c), as follows:
27 2025-2027 Principal Bonus Schedule
28 Statewide Growth Percentage Bonus
29 Top 5% $15,000
