37 to any regular wage or other bonus the principal receives or is scheduled to receive.
38 SECTION 7A.7.(c) Notwithstanding G.S. 135-1(7a), the bonuses awarded pursuant
39 to this section are not compensation under Article 1 of Chapter 135 of the General Statutes,
40 Retirement System for Teachers and State Employees.
41 SECTION 7A.7.(d) It is the intent of the General Assembly that funds provided
42 pursuant to this section will supplement principal compensation and not supplant local funds.
