1 SECTION 9D.1.(e) NC Pre-K Committees. – Local NC Pre-K committees shall use
2 the standard decision-making process developed by the Division of Child Development and Early
3 Education in awarding NC Pre-K classroom slots and student selection.
4 SECTION 9D.1.(f) Reporting. – The Division of Child Development and Early
5 Education shall submit an annual report no later than March 15 of each year to the Joint
6 Legislative Oversight Committee on Health and Human Services, the Office of State Budget and
7 Management, and the Fiscal Research Division. The report shall include the following:
