36 improvement. The Recommended State Budget may be presented in a format
37 chosen by the Director, except that the Recommended State Budget shall
38 clearly distinguish program base budget requirements, program reductions,
39 program eliminations, changes in program fund sources, program expansions,
40 and new programs, and shall explain all proposed capital improvements in the
41 context of the Six-Year Capital Improvements Plan and as required by
42 G.S. 143C-8-6.
